metadata.name: 8M 1/3333
metadata.description:
8M is a unique initiative that uses non-fungible tokens to raise funds for gender equality causes. The project features a digital artwork created by the Mexican artist @marinne343 with themes that challenge gender norms and celebrate the power of women. 

By purchasing one of these NFTs, buyers not only own a piece of digital art but also contribute to the cause of empowering women and promoting gender equality. 

The funds raised through this project are donated to organizations that work towards these goals.
